OL,3,CHome evacuated as roof collapses in
OL,4,CHastings
OL,6,FHouseholders have had a lucky escape
OL,7,Fin Hastings after their roof collapsed.
OL,9,FEast Sussex Fire and Rescue were
OL,10,Fcalled to the property on Ashburnham
OL,11,FRoad at 7. 38pm on Saturday, May 23rd.
OL,13,FTwo fire appliances, an aerial ladder
OL,14,Fplatform and two special appliances
OL,15,Fwere used to stabilise the building,
OL,16,Fbuut the road remains closed off.
OL,18,FThe fire service said all occupants
OL,19,Fwere evacuated and accounted for.
