OL,3,CHome evacuated as roof collapses in
OL,4,CHastings
OL,6,FCrews worked to make the scene safe
OL,7,Fand left the scene just before 10pm.
OL,9,FInvestigation work will now take place
OL,10,Fto establish what happened and make
OL,11,Fthe building safe.
OL,13,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,14,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,15,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,16,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
